string = os.linesep.join(['a = 10', 'b = 20', 'c = 30', '[section 1]',
    'sec1-a = 100', '    [section 1-1]',
    '    (list<int>) b = 1, 4, 8, 5, 9, 6, 4', '    sec1-1-a = 1000',
    '        [section 1-2-3]', '        something = else', '',
    '[section 2]', 'sec2-a = 20'])
config = ConfigParser(string)
config.write(self.config_path)
with open(self.config_path, 'r') as handler:
    self.assertEqual(string.strip(), handler.read().strip())
